an class=\"def\" hclass=\"def\" htag=\"span\">giving enthusiastic praise</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">a <span class=\"cl\">glowing account/report/review</span></span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">He spoke of her performance in the film <span class=\"cl\">in glowing terms</span> <span class=\"gloss\" hclass=\"gloss\" htag=\"span\">(= praising her highly)</span>.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">I’ve been hearing glowing reports about you.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">The show got glowing reviews from everyone.</span></li></ul><div class=\"collapse\" htag=\"div\" hclass=\"collapse\"><span class=\"unbox\" id=\"glowing_unbox_1\" unbox=\"snippet\"><span class=\"box_title\">Oxford Collocations Dictionary</span><span class=\"body\"><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"eb\">Glowing</span> is used with these nouns: <ul class=\"collocs_list\"><li class=\"li\" bord=\"n\">account</li><li class=\"li\" bord=\"n\">ash</li><li class=\"li\" bord=\"n\">cinder</li><li class=\"li\">…</li></ul></span><span class=\"xref_to_full_entry\">See <a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/collocations/glowing\" title=\" definition in Collocations\n \">full entry</a></span></span></span></div>    \n</li></ol><span class=\"dictlink-g\"><span class=\"dictlink\">See <a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/american_english/glowing\" title=\" definition in American English\n \"><span class=\"xh\">glowing</span></a> in the Oxford Advanced American Dictionary</span></span><div class=\"pron-link\">Check pronunciation:\n                        <a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/pronunciation/english/glowing\">glowing</a></div></div>\n","matches":["glowing"],"relatives":["glowing"],"nearBys":["glower noun","glower verb","glowing adjective","glowingly adverb","glow stick